----------------------------------------Basics----------------------------

. Python is a interpreted language.
. Python is a Object-oriented Programmimg language
. Python is a High-level programming language.
. Guido Van Rossum - invented python
. how python got it's name ? -
       Guido Van Rossum is a big fan for British comedy, Monty Python's Flying Circus
       
